    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Polymer Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Polymer engineering is a multidisciplinary field that focuses on the design, synthesis, processing, and application of polymeric materials. It combines principles of chemistry, materials science, and engineering to develop and optimize polymers with specific properties for various applications ranging from everyday consumer products to advanced medical devices and aerospace components.</p>
                    <p>As a polymer engineer, you'll work on creating new polymeric materials, improving existing ones, and developing efficient processing methods. You'll apply your knowledge of polymer structure-property relationships to design materials with tailored characteristics such as strength, flexibility, durability, and environmental resistance. This field requires a deep understanding of molecular structures and how they influence macroscopic properties.</p>
                    <p>With growing concerns about sustainability, polymer engineers are increasingly focused on developing biodegradable polymers, recycling technologies, and bio-based alternatives to petroleum-derived plastics, making this an exciting and evolving career path with significant environmental impact.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Areas Section -->
    <section class="section bg-dark" id="key-areas">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Areas of Study</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Polymer Engineering encompasses critical disciplines for developing and processing advanced polymeric materials:</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-atom"></i> Polymer Chemistry</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Synthesis and characterization of polymers at the molecular level.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Polymerization Methods</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Addition, condensation reactions</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Polymer Structure</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Chain architecture, molecular weight</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Characterization Techniques</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Spectroscopy, chromatography</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Polymer Processing</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Methods and technologies for converting raw polymers into finished products.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Extrusion</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Film, sheet, profile production</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Injection Molding</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Complex part manufacturing</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Additive Manufacturing</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">3D printing with polymers</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-microscope"></i> Polymer Physics</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Study of physical properties and behavior of polymeric materials.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Viscoelasticity</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Creep, stress relaxation</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Thermal Properties</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Glass transition, crystallinity</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Mechanical Behavior</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Strength, toughness, elasticity</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid three-columns" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-flask"></i> Polymer Composites</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Development and characterization of polymer-based composite materials.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Fiber Reinforcement</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Carbon, glass, natural fibers</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Nanocomposites</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Nanoclays, carbon nanotubes</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Interface Engineering</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Adhesion, compatibility</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-recycle"></i> Sustainable Polymers</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Development of environmentally friendly polymers and recycling technologies.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Biodegradable Polymers</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">PLA, PHA, starch-based</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Recycling Technologies</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Mechanical, chemical recycling</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Bio-based Polymers</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Cellulose, lignin derivatives</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> Polymer Modeling</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Computational methods for predicting polymer properties and behavior.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Molecular Dynamics</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Chain conformation, diffusion</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Process Simulation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Mold filling, extrusion</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Structure-Property Modeling</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">QSPR, machine learning</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

